It's a large sized labradorite skull that I used , comes with very nice blue flash . Even there's a line appearing through her left face , which doesn't make her flawless .but to me it represents uniqueness . This Princess is one of a kind ,including her imperfection !

I incorporated a bar prong setting with 
9x sky blue topaz , 
2x Pink Saphire ,
1x Chrome diopside,
and 2x garnet (in bowtie setting which of technique credit to Miles McDonald)

The piece is set in Sterling/Argentium/Fine siver , and some 14k yellow gold filled .
